{"tid":990753,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"【中港車】神技術！警告牌前照泊車　駛走仲要撞多嘢？","createTime":"2019-01-22T01:02:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T12:44:00.000Z","uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9985b12bf004d33d85fe011d68f30aa990e325d9","tid":990753,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T01:02:04.000Z","msg":"<strong>中港車神技術！警告牌前照泊車　駛走仲要撞多嘢？</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190122/bkn-20190122081529222-0122_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190122%2Fbkn-20190122081529222-0122_00822_001.html&d=Wqf%2BBtIb0uKZLQ16pRiKQSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=3d5b5a5b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190122/bkn-20190122081529222-0122_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n片LINK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：<a href=\"https://tv.on.cc/hk/index.html?i=ONS190121-14357-301-M&amp;d=1548043216\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftv.on.cc%2Fhk%2Findex.html%3Fi%3DONS190121-14357-301-M%26d%3D1548043216&d=Wqf%2BBtIb0uKZLQ16pRiKQSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=1faf5523\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tv.on.cc/hk/index.html?i=ONS190121-14357-301-M&amp;d=1548043216</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190122/photo/bkn-20190122081529222-0122_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190122081843\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190122%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190122081529222-0122_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190122081843&h=ab9cc7e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係咪真係睇唔到&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n駕車要時刻注意路面情況。惟近日有中港車在油站「不准泊車」的警告牌前泊車，離開時更撞向警告牌及雪糕筒。<br />\n<br />\n上周六（19日）在赤鱲角香港國際機場附近一個油站內，有中港車隨意停泊在油站後，司機匆忙落車往便利店方向走去。有趣的是該車前放着「不准泊車」的警告牌，並擺放了數個雪糕筒。<br />\n<br />\n當中港車司機駕車駛離油站時，疑看不到車前的阻礙物，竟徑直撞去，直至聽到「砰」的一聲始停車。司機徐徐倒車調整距離，再度駛離。有油站職員目擊一切後「𢱑爆頭」，將警告牌移回原處。<br />\n<br />\n有網民嘲諷：「遲早累街坊」、「佢哋真係大晒㗎喎」、「如果有小朋友喺度就死得」。"},{"pid":"61220f43bf793aecfbb2eaeaf0c364f164f4dc8f","tid":990753,"uid":60860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T03:12:24.000Z","msg":"Alphard中港車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53b1ef6e76f99618baf24df729f1ad71df46a6b0","tid":990753,"uid":13450,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T03:51:53.000Z","msg":"果d好多都搵食車 好多車停曬係油站<br />\nd警察做唔到野 但油站職員係唔會理<br />\n而你停係度油站d人又唔俾你停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c24c6648b9395e24c37e202817f9f062853c72fc","tid":990753,"uid":25148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T12:44:00.000Z","msg":"點解而家多左咁多馬路片係用濕鳩改歌做BGM"}]}